data.description: Closing costs negotiable with reasonable offer! This charming home boasts four bedrooms and two bathrooms, all on one level, and is situated on a large corner lot. Come and enjoy the Timberlake Community with events, walking trails, two swimming pools, multiple playgrounds, a fishing pier, and tennis courts. Location is a plus for quick access to the freeways, Town Center, Mount Trashmore, and Military bases.
